## OpenCode-specific

- **Agents**: `plan` runs Fable, `build` runs local MLX (Qwen3.6-27B), and the
  read-only `review` subagent runs Sonnet. Switch with `/agent <name>` in the TUI.
- **Full-auto mode**: build and plan agents run without permission prompts. The
  `review` subagent remains read-only and rejects unmatched shell commands.
- **MCP**: generated into the `mcp` block of opencode.json from the shared
  `packages/mcp-servers.txt` registry. Every generated tool namespace is enabled.
- **Plugin events** (for reference, when adding new plugins): `session.created`,
  `session.idle`, `tool.execute.before`/`.after`, `file.edited`, `permission.asked`.
  Plugins live in `~/.config/opencode/plugin/*.ts` (Bun-executed; `$` is Bun shell).
